            "minimumOsVersion": "15.0",
            "releaseNotes": "- Media controls for background tabs -\nIf a tab is playing audio in a background tab, the user will be able to mute/unmute the tab from the search or tab bar, by long pressing the tab icon, or from inside the Tabs overview. In order to find the playing tab, there is an animation on the tab inside the Tab view and a pulse on the tab icon. There is also a mute/unmute icon in the search bar. Finally, if a tab is muted and you want to unmute it quickly, you can just press the device volume up/down buttons.\n\n- Improved Sync and Backup -\nBookmarks, Tabs and Passwords will sync quicker both ways.\nImproved status info in Account and Sync settings\nAdded onboarding for sync and backup and easy account sign in/up\n\n- Bug fixes and UI improvements -\nFile and image upload in search for AI queries\nNew languages (Estonian, Malay (Malaysia), Burmese, Burmese (Zawgyi), Sinhala, Slovenian, Swahili, Tamil and Tagalog/Filipino)\nHot fix: Crash fixes x 4 (in 6.6.1)",
